n your customized plan. If you\'re not satisfied, our maids will come back and clean whatever area didn\'t meet your expectations. Simply notify us within 24-hours. <b>Read More </b></p>','Why Diana's House Cleaning Services?','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision-v1','','','2014-01-07 07:28:41','2014-01-07 07:28:41','',28,'http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/uncategorized/28-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
