	(59,1,'2014-01-07 07:50:50','2014-01-07 07:50:50','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/residential-Commercial-Cleaning.jpg\" animation=\"left\" /][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]<h4><strong>Customized housekeeping service. Your home - your cleaning package.</strong></h4><p>Residential  and Commercial house cleaning services from Diana's House Cleaning Services revolve around you. It\'s your home, after all, so Diana's House Cleaning Services cleans it your way with a plan designed specifically with your cleaning preferences in mind. Whether your children have allergies, or you prefer green home cleaning, Diana's House Cleaning Services offers house cleaning options that meet your needs. Each Cleaning Team works with you, making Diana's House Cleaning Services one of the most flexible professional cleaning companies out there.</p><p><strong> </strong></p><p>At Diana's House Cleaning Services, our goal is open communication between Cleaning Teams and customers. Making you comfortable, listening to your needs and encouraging your feedback makes us an even better home cleaning service, while also ensuring the most accurate, in-home estimates. We know challenging economic times may mean creating a package around your priority rooms. Our home cleaning services are not one size fits all – they\'re customized to fit your needs and your budget.</p><p><strong>How are we doing?</strong></p><p>This is a question you\'ll hear from your Cleaning Teams<b> </b>and their supervisors. We listen and make changes to your housekeeping service to better meet your family\'s needs.</p><h4> </h4><p>For a flexible, professional cleaning company who listens, find your <b>local Diana's House Cleaning Services</b><b> Cleaning Team</b>. We\'d love to meet you and provide a free, no-obligation <b>in-home estimate. </b>Or tell us