	(296,1,'2014-01-13 13:58:49','2014-01-13 13:58:49','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"3_4\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/happy-family-on-the-floor.jpg\" animation=\"left\" /][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]\r\n\r\nWelcome to Diana's House Cleaning Services. We are a dedicated leader in the house cleaning industry with a firm commitment to protecting your home and the environment. Our cleaning team has been providing high quality residential and commercial cleaning services for over 25 years and we have built a reputation for providing reliable maid services at competitive prices. Our optional Detail-Clean Rotation System gives you peace of mind as we give your home a deep, detailed professional house cleaning all year long.\r\n\r\n<b>Affordable. Reliable. Thorough. Home Cleaning Services. </b>\r\n\r\nAt Diana's House Cleaning Services, our goal is to provide top quality residential house cleaning at the best possible price. Our cleaning professionals have participated in extensive training and are fully bonded and insured. They show up on time with the right supplies and get right to work. Get your free estimate for house cleaning services at 425-652-5252 today.\r\n\r\n<b>Satisfaction Guarantee</b>\r\n\r\nYour satisfaction is important to us and we guarantee that you will be satisfied with the quality of our home cleaning services, or you can contact us. We will return the next day and clean it again at no additional cost. Please browse our website to learn more about our maid cleaning services and the benefits of green cleaning for the environment and your health and call us today for a<a title=\"free estimate\" href=\" http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/get-a-free-estimate/\" target=\"_blank\"> FREE estimate</a>.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_testimonial admin_label=\"Testimonial\" url_new_windo