b>YOUR HOME -YOUR CUSTOM CLEANING PLAN.</b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">We clean your home the way you want. That means our professional maid services are designed with your needs in mind. We listen and provide customized plans that make you proud of your clean, fresh home.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><b>QUALITY CLEAN GUARANTEED.</b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Your satisfaction is our guarantee. At Diana's House Cleaning Services our professional maids clean based on your customized plan. If you\'re not satisfied, our maids will come back and clean whatever area didn\'t meet your expectations. Simply notify us within 24-hours.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><b>24 Hour Guarantee</b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-35\" alt=\"24-hour-cleaning-guarantee\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/24-hour-cleaning-guarantee.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><b>Quality Clean Guaranteed.</b>\r\nYour satisfaction is our guarantee. At Diana's House Cleaning Services our professional maids clean based on your customized plan. If you\'re not satisfied, our maids will come back and clean whatever area didn\'t meet your expectations. Simply notify us within 24-hours.</p>\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Successful-Cleaning-People-.jpg\" animation=\"left\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_testimonial admin_label=\"Testimonial\" author=\"Allan\" url_new_window=\"off\"]\r\n<h3>Our customers are talking</h3>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"Trustworthy, reliable and very good at their job. I\'m a fan!\"</em></blockquote>\r\n[/et_pb_testimonial][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Get-your-free-quote-button.png\" url=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/get-a-free-estimate/\" animation=\"left\" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Why Us?','','inherit','open','