	(391,1,'2014-04-16 12:40:12','2014-04-16 12:40:12','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"3_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]\r\n<p align=\"left\"><b>Your Fresh Start Starts Here. </b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Come join Diana's House Cleaning Services and begin your path to a rewarding career with one of North America’s leading residential cleaning services! To get started, simply click Search Cleaning Jobs for employment opportunities with Diana's House Cleaning Services in your area.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Benefits of a position with Diana's House Cleaning Services:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Among the highest paid cleaning positions in the business</li>\r\n	<li>Employee benefits</li>\r\n	<li>Paid travel time and costs</li>\r\n	<li>No night or weekend work</li>\r\n	<li>A great training program (no experience necessary)</li>\r\n	<li>The confidence of working with environmentally preferred cleaning products</li>\r\n	<li>The satisfaction of being part of an “elite team”</li>\r\n	<li>The excitement of knowing you’re starting a career with a very successful, growing company with real opportunities for advancement in the system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align=\"left\"> At Diana's House Cleaning Services, our employees are “cleaning up!” When you do a great job, you will find the career opportunities you have been looking for. In fact, right the start, new hires are put on a personal development system that will see them go from Professional Housecleaners to  Team Leaders to General Managers to Franchise Managers in a short period of time.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Your on-the-job experience and loyalty is important and Diana's House Cleaning Services is committed to promoting talent from within. The day you join, you’re automatically put on a <a title=\"Career Opportunity Path\" href=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/career-opportunity-path/\">Career Opportunity Path</a>. You start by participating in a series of professional training programs, which include classroom and video training, followed by actual on-the-job experience. As your job knowledge and experience increases, you’ll have the chance to be promoted through the Career Opportunity Path. If you’re a team player, have a great attitude, possess a strong work ethic, and are committed to excellence, then we would love to work with you! Please fill out our brief online application form and we will get back to you within one business day.</p>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Careers','','inherit','open','open','','192-revision-v1','','','2014-04-16 12:40:12','2014-04-16 12:40:12','',192,'http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/192-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
