	(458,1,'2014-05-08 03:00:09','2014-05-08 03:00:09','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"3_4\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/FB-BANNER-414.png\" url=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/get-a-free-estimate/\" animation=\"left\" /][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" /][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]\r\n\r\nWelcome to Diana's House Cleaning Services. We are a dedicated leader in the house cleaning industry with a firm commitment to protecting your home and the environment. Our cleaning team has been providing high quality residential and commercial cleaning services with a combined experience of over 25 years, and we have built a reputation for providing reliable maid services at competitive prices. Our optional Detail-Clean Rotation System gives you peace of mind as we give your home a deep, detailed professional house cleaning all year long.\r\n\r\n<b>Affordable. Reliable. Thorough. Home Cleaning Services. </b>\r\n\r\nAt Diana's House Cleaning Services, our goal is to provide top quality residential house cleaning at the best possible price. Our cleaning professionals have participated in extensive training and are fully bonded and insured. They show up on time with the right supplies and get right to work. Get your free estimate for house cleaning services at 425-652-5252 today.\r\n\r\n<b>Satisfaction Guarantee</b>\r\n\r\nYour satisfaction is important to us and we guarantee that you will be satisfied with the quality of our home cleaning services, or you can contact us. We will return the next day and clean it again at no additional cost. Please browse our website to learn more about our maid cleaning services and call us today for a<a title=\"free estimate\" href=\" http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/get-a-free-estimate/\" target=\"_blank\"> FREE estimate</a>.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_testimonial admin_label=\"Testimonial\" url_new_window=\"on\" author=\"Amy\"]\r\n<h3>Our customers are talking</h3>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"I am truly impressed with the work Diana's House Cleaning Services does and appreciate the personal touches.\"</em></blockquote>\r\n[/et_pb_testimonial][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"Call To Action\" title=\"call us\" button_url=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/get-a-free-estimate/\" button_text=\"for your free estimate\" background_color=\"#7ebec5\" use_background_color=\"on\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"center\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/get-a-free-estimate/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/telephone.png\" alt=\"telephone\" width=\"231\" height=\"231\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-05-08 03:00:09','2014-05-08 03:00:09','',2,'http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(462,1,'2014-05-08 07:32:26','2014-05-08 07:32:26','[et_pb_section][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]<p><strong>We clean. You save. They smile...</strong></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/541038_550486234985946_448956430_n.jpg\" animation=\"left\" /][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\"]<p class=\"p2\">The <strong>Sunshine Kids Foundation</strong> adds quality of life to children with cancer by providing them with exciting, positive group activities, so they may once again do what kids are supposed to do . . . have fun and celebrate life!</p><p class=\"p2\">The Sunshine Kids Foundation was founded by Rhoda Tomasco in 1982 while she was serving as a volunteer in the pediatric cancer unit of a hospital in Houston, Texas. After seeing the loneliness and depression among children during their extended hospital treatments, Rhoda had a vision to provide these young cancer patients with opportunities to participate in positive group activities which promoted self-esteem , personal accomplishment and just plain old fashioned fun! Today, that vision has been realized many times over, as thousands of children from hospitals across the country have reaped the benefits of The Sunshine Kids Foundation’s many programs and national and regional events. Funded by personal contributions, corporations and foundations, the Sunshine Kids continues, as it has since its inception, to provide all of its activities completely free of charge to the children’s families and hospitals. (www.sunshinekids.org)</p><p class=\"p2\">This year, our organization is working to generate as much support as we can to support their good work. From <strong>May 1 through July 31, get 15% off</strong> of your cleaning service, and 15% of all the profits we make go to the Sunshine Kids Foundation. Call us now at 425.224.5534 for a free quote and mention Promo Code: \"Sunshine\" for your discount.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"Call To Action\" title=\"425.224.5534\" button_text=\"425.224.5534\" background_color=\"#5f768e\" use_background_color=\"on\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"center\"]<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-482 size-full\" src=\"http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/save151.png\" alt=\"save15\" width=\"289\" height=\"288\" /></p>[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Community Work','','publish','open','open','','community-work','','','2014-06-17 18:04:28','2014-06-17 18:04:28','',0,'http://www.mops-n-buckets.com/?page_id=462',0,'page','',0),
